{"tid":1641454,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"保安俾人拉抵撚死","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T13:19:08.000Z","uid":189309,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9946726d70aea0b3fb287d2e24970724ae68a10d","tid":1641454,"uid":189309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:40:04.000Z","msg":"屌唒你班香港人幾時先捨得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工</span></span>，根本而家面對呢個極權政府最好嘅辦法就係罷工。<br />\n<br />\n但係偏偏香港人就唔想罷工只想被罷工，幾時先可以真正一個大型罷工，今日咁樣拉人已經足夠原因去罷工，但係要叫香港人罷工難過出解放軍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攝高枕頭諗清楚<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">輸撚左我哋會點</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53608391ec3345e0dd8c6e7b5243bc20a777a1ca","tid":1641454,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:41:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲都得個講字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a19669470cb9ee0de123c54981d874f536ecdf","tid":1641454,"uid":264495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"你要香港人唔返工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553052800210d408dbe823a826151e491fc0d2df","tid":1641454,"uid":189309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30a19669470cb9ee0de123c54981d874f536ecdf","tid":1641454,"uid":264495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"你要香港人唔返工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"明白嘅死老竇都仲要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"